  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">From 11th level, you are at peace with your nature and you are not afraid of it, obtaining some benefits:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you roll for initiative, you gain 1 impetus for every personality trait that derives from your family instinct.</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You no longer lose control if all your personality traits have been replaced by instincts.</span></li>\n<li><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you suffer a trauma, on the other hand, you lose a trait of instinct, replacing it with a related personality trait. You can try to regain their instinct as they would normally regain your personality traits.</span></li>\n</ul>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
    "source": "Historia Manuale pagina: 183",
